{"id":180732,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/09/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-2011921/","date":"2011-09-22T05:00:36Z","modified":"2011-09-22T05:00:36Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐 &#8211; 2011/9/21","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><b>(</b></span><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/yigroup\">@yigroup</a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/xiaomi2020\">@xiaomi2020</a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【时政热点】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">东亚论坛：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.eastasiaforum.org/2011/09/20/not-the-next-arab-spring-the-china-method-for-managing-popular-unrest/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国并非下一个“阿拉伯之春”：具有中国特色的管理群众骚动方式</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国政府对抗以活动软硬兼施的策略，加上强大的宣传机器，使其统治得以延续</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">东亚论坛：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.eastasiaforum.org/2011/09/21/nationalism-and-where-it-might-lead/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的民族主义及其前景</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——随着改革的进行，中国的民族主义会对它的外交政策产生重大影响，其前景有五种可能。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">半岛新闻：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.aljazeera.net/asia/2011/09/21/chinas-land-grabs-case-study\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国强征</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">农民</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">土地的一个个案</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——柳下庄的农民一夜之间发现自己失去了土地，但国家的补偿他们却一分钱都没有见到</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交学者》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/china-power/2011/09/21/decoding-social-management/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">解析中国的“社会管理”</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——这是继“和谐社会”和“科学发展”之后的又一个新名词，说明中国领导人认为必须主动出击，防患于未然。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华盛顿邮报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.washingtonpost.com/local/dc-politics/md-casino-developer-courts-wealthy-chinese-by-offering-green-card-in-exchange-for-500000-investment/2011/09/19/gIQAyAgjgK_story.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">马里兰州赌场开发商用五十万美元投资换取绿卡的条件招徕中国富人</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——考虑到一家三口的绿卡和孩子今后的教育，五十万美元的代价似乎不算太高</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">彭博新闻：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-20/china-endorsing-tobacco-in-schools-adds-to-10-trillion-gdp-cost.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国允许烟草公司“赞助”学校，可能会造成</span>10<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">万亿美元的经济损失</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——虽然烟草公司做广告受到限制，但是它们对学校的“赞助”却在培养新的烟民</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国听说博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.chinahearsay.com/under-pressure-from-regulators-sina%E2%80%99s-chief-comes-up-with-really-stupid-idea/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">在监管部门压力下，新浪负责人想出昏招</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——新浪微博表示要开发用户信用系统，简化内容管理流程。但这毫无意义，也起不了作用</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20110921/pl_nm/us_usa_china_currency\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">为解决</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">工作机会匮乏</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">问题，</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国参议院拿人民币开刀</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——声望低迷的美国国会打算以增加就业为名提出对人民币施压的议案，虽然奥巴马的就业提案中并不包括这个内容</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【国际外交】</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《大西洋》月刊：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.theatlantic.com/international/archive/2011/09/will-china-make-the-world-safe-for-democracy/245411/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国出手拯救欧洲，对于自由贸易而言是件好事</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——想象一下，你有一位经营公社的共产主义朋友，忽然她打算投资期货，以便挣钱扩大公社规模，印刷更多的马克思主义宣传材料。。。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亚洲观察哨：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.asiasentinel.com/index.php?option=com_content&#038;task=view&#038;id=3771&#038;Itemid=422\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国在债务问题上咄咄逼人</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——欧洲因债务危机向中国求救，中国自然开出了自己的价码。如果它借此机会拱卒过河，那欧洲人只能怪自己不争气。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/09/22/opinion/22iht-edshapiro22.html?partner=rssnyt&#038;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国是如何赶走游客的？</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——想要了解美国是如何坐失亚洲财富爆炸所带来的良机，只需看看法国是如何大把从他们身上捞钱的就知道了。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【经济金融】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/chinarealtime/2011/09/21/imf-a-little-more-worried-about-china/?mod=WSJBlog\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">国际货币基金对中国有点不放心</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——据它估算，中国的国内贷款数额到六月底相当于</span></span><span><span>GDP</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">的</span></span><span><span>173%</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，远高于类似收入的发展中国家水平。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/09/20/uk-boc-swaps-idUSTRE78J0SZ20110920\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国银行停止和欧洲某些银行的外汇互换交易</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——由于担心会被欧洲的债务危机拖累，中行停止了与瑞士和法国几家银行的外汇交易</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-09-21/china-faces-hot-money-surge-on-financial-market-turmoil.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">金融市场动荡令中国面临热钱涌入</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——资金流入会使中央银行抑制通胀和削减房地产泡沫的努力更加困难，增加人民币升值压力。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《金融时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.ft.com/beyond-brics/2011/09/21/us-v-china-which-is-hardest-to-enter/#axzz1Ycy0Si8Y\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">对</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：谁的市场更难进入？</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——根据对全球商业领袖的问卷调查，美国市场在发达国家中最难进入，但中国比美国市场更难进入</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110921/ap_on_bi_ge/as_china_aviation\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">波音公司设计新飞机时照顾到中国市场</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——在今后</span></span><span><span>20</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年间，中国将从购买五千架商用飞机，成为世界第二大航空市场。波音希望能拿到其中一半的订单</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【生活百态】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国见红博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://seeingredinchina.com/2011/09/21/social-obligations-and-the-meaning-of-meals/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">社交义务与请客的意义</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——在中国，“关系”的重要性使得每个人都背着社交义务，而吃饭也不仅仅是吃饭那么简单</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《每日电讯报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/8776515/The-rise-and-rise-of-Mandarin-but-how-many-will-end-up-speaking-it.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中文越来越热门，但到底有多少人会说它？</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——自</span></span><span><span>2005</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年以来，中国在全球开设了</span></span><span><span>300</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">多家孔子学院，每年派出五千教师，但成效仍有待检验</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《金融时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.ft.com/beyond-brics/2011/09/20/chinas-fast-moving-car-buyers/#axzz1Ycy0Si8Y\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国购车者的兴趣变化迅速</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——他们喜欢名牌，但是并不固定，让他们满意不是件容易事。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<div><i>发送邮件至 yyyyiiii+subscribe@googlegroups.com 即可订阅译文；译者的音频博客已登录iTunes，到<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/id453722327?ign-mpt=uo%3D4\">这里</a>即可收听往期的译者音频节目；下载更新需翻墙。</i><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-7846706708134068457?l=yyyyiiii.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\"